{"tid":1150400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯普京冰球賽後繞場揮手 被紅地毯絆倒失威","createTime":"2019-05-11T20:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T23:59:00.000Z","uid":125193,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97f511c3d84f852df62979a04002e67e1275e9a3","tid":1150400,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T20:48:18.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯總統普京向來以強人姿態示人，形象威風凜凜，但周五他落場打冰上曲棍球時卻出醜人前，在繞場向觀眾揮手時被絆倒，可謂老貓燒鬚。<br />\n<br />\n周五在索契舉行的明星冰球賽中，普京一隊以14比7贏得球賽，他個人更攻入8球。當他賽後與隊友繞場答謝觀眾支持時，沒察覺冰球場上一角放了紅地毯，結果被絆倒向前趴在地上，但他很快就站起來，似乎沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n66歲的普京一向愛展示好動有活力一面，包括與總理梅德韋傑夫一起運動、在索契滑雪或在黑海潛水，他亦多次與政府官員、商人甚至職業好手打冰球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnfDbqK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnfDbqK.jpg&h=2d247a0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d6eacf9586ac9bdbf53e1a41863c0d8c871129b","tid":1150400,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T21:04:21.000Z","msg":"馬總統看水錶"},{"pid":"8a04c5d42619576c21884f8ba3e1453b013a4738","tid":1150400,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T22:19:49.000Z","msg":"On9抵撚死 俾人恥笑成世啦閪京<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a037c2c8e7b467ee11fd78281723f08d7db5f0","tid":1150400,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T23:37:47.000Z","msg":"冰上面有地墊係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740eb0d519a9b39ffdbf3f38c530245e3563a94a","tid":1150400,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a037c2c8e7b467ee11fd78281723f08d7db5f0","tid":1150400,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T23:37:47.000Z","msg":"冰上面有地墊係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T23:40:04.000Z","msg":"怕凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔撚會咩"},{"pid":"a030f59e21827d5e62c848799991b6f84